<i>#No such number ##</i>

864
02:13:23,900 --> 02:13:25,700
Hello!

865
02:13:30,300 --> 02:13:32,100
Hello!

866
02:13:37,800 --> 02:13:39,700
[Whistles]

867
02:13:40,000 --> 02:13:42,000
FedEx!

868
02:14:19,600 --> 02:14:21,500
[Door Alarm Beeping]

869
02:14:49,600 --> 02:14:52,600
- You look lost.
- I do?

870
02:14:52,900 --> 02:14:55,000
Where are you headed?

871
02:14:58,800 --> 02:15:00,600
Well, I was just about
to figure that out.

872
02:15:02,500 --> 02:15:04,600
Well, that's 83 South.

873
02:15:04,900 --> 02:15:08,700
<i>And this road here will
hook you up with l-40 East.</i>

874
02:15:08,900 --> 02:15:11,100
If you turn right,

875
02:15:11,300 --> 02:15:14,800
that'll take you to
Amarillo, Flagstaff,

876
02:15:15,100 --> 02:15:16,900
California.

877
02:15:18,100 --> 02:15:20,000
And if you head back
that direction,

878
02:15:20,100 --> 02:15:23,000
<i>you'll find a whole lotta nothin'
all the way to Canada.</i>

879
02:15:25,200 --> 02:15:27,000
I got it.

880
02:15:27,200 --> 02:15:29,300
All right, then.

881
02:15:32,000 --> 02:15:33,800
Good luck, cowboy.

882
